Product description

Saving Space
Compatible for Google Home Mini and Mini 2, UGREEN wall mount hanger enables you to put your home mini on the wall for convenient placement, especially when your counter or tabletop space is already overcrowded.
An ideal choice to bracket the mini speaker onto the wall near the socket, making the space neat and clean.

Mount Securely
With strong adhesive on the back and 2 screws included, this speaker mount can hang your nest mini speaker securely with no hassle.

Easy to Use
Simple installation by sticking and screwing this sturdy holder onto your wall.
Note: Please remember to install this mount with screws for more stable installation.
Remember to clean your wall before you stick and screw this wall mount and wait for 24h before usage.

No Blocking for Charger
Space saved on the bottom enables you to connect the wall charger to charge home mini freely.

Premium Quality
Made of high-quality ABS material, this speaker mount is stable, fade-less and non-deforming.
Silicone pads on the inner side, protect the mini home speaker from scratches.

      Forrest Ruby
      3.0 out of 5 stars Does exactly what it describes but that's the problem
      Reviewed in the United States on December 17, 2020
      Verified Purchase
      This item does exactly what it advertises. It installs on the wall easily and perfectly cradles your Google Home Mini. What I discovered very quickly though is that mounting the Mini on the wall with the speaker pointing not up, but horizontally substantially changed my ease of use and enjoyment of the sound. The Mini is designed primarily to broadcast sound upward which will fill a large space. When pointed horizontally a lot of the warmth in the sound goes away and it becomes far more directional. Walls have a lot more distorting shapes (book shelves, media centers) and sound deadening (curtains, wall hangings). I also found that the microphone for pickup of my commands was also detrimentally affected by the change in orientation. I found I had to be facing the device while speaking much more than I had before.
      Overall, its a great idea and it does exactly what it was designed to do. I just don't know if its the right solution for most people.

      H. Cole
      5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install, fits mini perfectly, very strong adhesive
      Reviewed in the United States on June 15, 2019
      Verified Purchase
      It took only 30 seconds to install this mount including unboxing, since I used the adhesive. Although it came with screws I chose to use the adhesive assuming that it would be less damaging to the wall. The box and packaging was very professional and came in a similar design style to the actual Google Home Mini box.

      However the adhesive is very strong, perhaps too strong, as one knock test showed me, so I am not sure if what I assumed is correct, but be careful when mounting because it is very difficult to get it off if you used the adhesive.

      I would suggest you thread the cord through the bottom if the outlet is below the mount. This removes unnecessary stress on the cable. You can fix the upside down LEDs via your mini's device settings on the Google Home app.

      Overall an amazing product, I would definitely recommend this to a friend.
